            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Чтобы использовать переменную в условии цикла while, объявите её вне блока кода.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Now Playing: Ryan Paris&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"3\" /><option startIndex=\"4\" endIndex=\"15\" /><option startIndex=\"16\" endIndex=\"17\" /><option startIndex=\"18\" endIndex=\"22\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Now Playing: Ryan Paris\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>var</code>, затем <code>keepPlaying</code>, а затем <code>=</code>, <code>true</code>.</p></body></html>"
